summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Twentieth Avenue N.W. from Canre Place to West 75th Street et al in the City of Seattle, by laying water mains under Ordinance No. 21188, creating Local Improvement District No. 2094 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
